data.description: Be the Envy of all of your neighbors as you sit on just over an acre, with one of the BEST back decks in all of Chaddwyck! With plenty of space to entertain, and a Peaceful view THIS is the home for you! Welcome Home to Chaddwyck, an established neighborhood in Oconee County School District situated near Athens Academy!! When you visit 1220 Chaddwyck you will find a beautiful home tucked away among a stunning array of mature hardwoods, on a private lot with over an acre of land. The home itself has 4 bed/2.5bath AND an oversized Finished BONUS room. As you enter, the foyer will greet you with beautiful hardwood floors, and from there the living room boasts tall vaulted ceilings and a gas log fireplace; the perfect space for entertaining or relaxing after work with a good book or movie. If you love an open eat-in kitchen, this home is sure to impress with Stainless Steel Appliances, Granite Countertops, a breakfast nook, and room for a custom coffee bar all seperate from the formal dining room (or flex space). Does morning coffee, or a night cap outside overlooking a peaceful terrace sound wonderful? You will love the spacious, private back deck right off the kitchen. This space has more than enough room to relax, or entertain your friends and family. The Deck overlooks the back of the property and the firepit sitting area with access to the terrace. While you may have neighbors, you would never know it - this property is private and beautifully kept with space enough for the storage shed and/or a swimming pool. Back inside, The Owner's Suite is on the Main level. It includes a spacious walk-in closet, a private bath complete with shower and separate soaking tub, and tray ceilings for an added touch of luxury. Upstairs you will find 3 additional bedrooms, a full bath, and the oversized BONUS room. The bedrooms are spacious, and private with plenty of closet storage, while the bonus room is perfect for a home gym, office, game room, musician's media space, or as an additional bedroom. This Chaddwyck home & Subdivision filled with beautiful hardwoods, large private lots, amazing location, an OPTIONAL HOA, have so much to offer. We can't wait for you to see it. Schedule your showing today.
